// seliason, amillner, cwilson, dthatcher, klisonbee, wharper, lfillmore,
// mballard, kgrover and nthurston — each with 2–3 sourced highlights, a
// `tags` array, and a one-line `spotlightTheme`. A follow-up structuring pass
// backfilled the same human-readable `tags` (Consistency, Notable Actions,
// Public Statements, Rhetoric vs Reality, Positive Leadership, Public Behavior)
// onto every original national figure too, so all 35 officials are now
// uniformly categorized, tagged and themed.
//
// A later June 2026 "Relevant to Me" pass added 10 more legislators keyed on the
