      facts: 'Eliason repeatedly partnered with shooting-sports and gun-rights figures on safe-storage and gun-lock measures, saying “everybody can agree on the culture of safety.”',
      why: 'Finding cross-interest common ground on a polarizing issue reflects pragmatic, principled leadership.',
