      headline: 'Pattern: a 20-year education-and-workforce throughline from campus to Capitol',
      facts: 'Millner’s public identity and her record point the same direction across two decades: she led Weber State for ten years and stepped down on the schedule she set, then built a Senate portfolio centered on the same education, workforce and Northern Utah economic-development priorities.',
