      facts: 'Defay’s early record shows a pattern of pragmatism over partisanship — carrying a Democratic senator’s child-marriage bill to a near-unanimous vote and framing her work around anti-coercion protections — even as her family-business leadership role stays a standing conflict area to watch on related votes.',
